{
  "stem": "18637.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 426.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody survived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were married already.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had children.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The-- the-- the aunt what used to help us, she had five children.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Nobody survived-- with her husband.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The other one didn't have children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So she got killed, with her husband.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean-- but we were already the lucky ones having a sister and a brother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It wasn't-- And, you know, as I look back, I am happy I helped in any way I could.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "At that time, even a meal-- when I was cooking, and somebody came, and I gave a meal, they'll never forget me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "If I ever had a an extra shirt, and I gave it to somebody, they'll never forget it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And even here, whoever comes, they don't go to a hotel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They come right here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They know they're welcome.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "When we-- when I come to Israel or come to New York, it's more than a sister comes to them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because I always had help-- gave a help-- a help as much as I could.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I was-- myself, I couldn't help.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But that you have a good feeling that you weren't selfish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And you were-- you understand-- you understood life, what it's all about.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You saw it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So that's--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we stayed till we came here, in 1948, in February, with General Sturgis.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [LAUGHS] it's a beautiful country.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How can you not like Canada?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How could you say something?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We came.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We worked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I worked, too.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My husband worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had children.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My-- my children are all university graduated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They all work as professionals.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have four, three daughters and a son.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they are married.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they have children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, we had some misfortunate thing with my grandson.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But like I said, life from then is not the same.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
